{
  "stem": "24231.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the peels, I would bring a wagon there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they would throw these peels into these wagons.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I would take it into the field as a compost.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But when these people-- these people came for this-- from these death marches, they brought them into these-- into these barracks.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I came to pick up these peels.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And as I came out from these-- from this cellar with the-- with the horses up, all of a sudden, everybody started to run towards those peels.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I was afraid that I'm going to run somebody over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I just stopped, took the horses out, left the wagon there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and when I came back in an hour, all the rotten peels and all the peels just disappeared.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People just ate it, because they were from death march.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They-- they were just hungry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I picked up the empty wagon and just went-- went home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- Were there other sections of the camp, particularly toward the end of the war, where there were non-Jews, or did it stay Jewish?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it stayed Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was outsiders.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, outside of camp, there was a-- this [NON-ENGLISH], the little-- little fortress, which was political prisoners.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were also some Jews in there, but they were politically-- politically-- they were captured for some political reasons or for-- for no reason at all, sometimes.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they were over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That-- I went into that place only once.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was at the end of the war when they started-- the Germans-- started to shoot some of these prisoners.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this was in May.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I had to bring my wagon, a flat, flat wagon.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
